Description: A simple regression testing framework for LFE.

Compile
-------
     erl -noshell -pa $LFE_PATH \
         -eval 'code:load_file(demo).' \
         -eval 'io:format("~n~p~n",[demo:start()]).' -s erlang halt

Run tests
---------
     erl -noshell -pa $LFE_PATH \
         -eval 'code:load_file(demo).' \
         -eval 'io:format("~n~p~n",[demo:start()]).' -s erlang halt

Output
------
Current test report:
bash-3.2$ c

{ok,demo,[]}
bash-3.2$ r
false

[[success,4],[fail,0]]
bash-3.2$ exit

("false" is printed when the false case is tested.)